{"title":"JQ中几种常见的方法","slug":"JQ中几种常见的方法","date":"2018-11-08T11:14:31.064Z","updated":"2018-11-08T12:01:09.509Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/JQ中几种常见的方法.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":null,"covers":null,"content":"<blockquote><p>1.属性操作<br>attr()可以用来更改元素节点的属性<br>removeAttr()移除元素节点的属性<br>实例代码如下</p>\n</blockquote>\n<figure class=\"highlight gams\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">var <span class=\"symbol\">$</span>para =<span class=\"symbol\">$</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"p\"</span>);\t\t\t\t<span class=\"comment\">//获取&lt;p&gt;节点</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">var p_txt =<span class=\"symbol\">$</span>para.attr(<span class=\"string\">\"title\"</span>)；\t\t<span class=\"comment\">//获取&lt;p&gt;节点的title属性</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"symbol\">$</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"p\"</span>).para.attr(<span class=\"string\">\"title\"</span>)；\t\t<span class=\"comment\">//移除&lt;p&gt;节点的title属性</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<blockquote><p>2.样式操作<br>attr()方法也可以用来设置元素节点的属性<br>addClass()方法是用来追加样式的<br>removeClass() 将匹配的元素删除全部或者指定的Class<br>toggle()    控制行为上的重复切换<br>实例代码如下</p>\n</blockquote>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;p <span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span></span>=<span class=\"string\">\"myClass\"</span> title=<span class=\"string\">\"选择你最喜欢的水果\"</span>&gt;你最喜欢的水果是?<span class=\"xml\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">p</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">var</span> p_class =$(<span class=\"string\">\"p\"</span>).attr(<span class=\"string\">\"class\"</span>);\t\t\t<span class=\"comment\">//获取p元素的Class</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$(<span class=\"string\">\"p\"</span>).attr(<span class=\"string\">\"class\"</span>,<span class=\"string\">\"high\"</span>);\t\t\t\t<span class=\"comment\">//将p元素的Class设置为high</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">$(<span class=\"string\">\"p\"</span>).addClass(<span class=\"string\">\"XXXX\"</span>);\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"comment\">//给&lt;p&gt;元素追加XXXX类</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$(<span class=\"string\">\"p\"</span>).removeClass(<span class=\"string\">\"XXXX\"</span>);\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"comment\">//给&lt;p&gt;元素移除XXXX类</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">$toggleBtn.toggle(<span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span>(<span class=\"params\"></span>)</span>&#123;\t\t\t\t<span class=\"comment\">//toggle()交换一组动作 具体例子 </span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"comment\">//显示元素   代码1</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;,<span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span>(<span class=\"params\"></span>)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"comment\">//隐藏元素\t代码2</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<blockquote><p>判断是否含有某个样式 hasClass() 如果有返回true 否则返回flase<br>html()方法相当于JavaScript中的innerHTML属性 可以用来读取或者设置某个元素中的HTML内容<br>text()方法当于JavaScript中的innerText属性   可以用来读取或者设置某个元素中的文本内容<br>val()方法当于JavaScript中的value属性        可以用来设置和获取元素的值 在表单中经常用来选中<br>focus()方法当于JavaScript中的onfocus()方法是处理获得焦点时的事件<br>blur()方法当于JavaScript中的onblur()方法是处理失去焦点时的事件</p>\n</blockquote>\n<figure class=\"highlight fsharp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$(<span class=\"string\">\"/*选择器选中下拉列表框*/\"</span>).<span class=\"keyword\">val</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"/*其中某一项*/\"</span>)\t\t\t<span class=\"comment\">//可以更改或者设置默认项</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$(<span class=\"string\">\"/*选择器选中多选框*/\"</span>).<span class=\"keyword\">val</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"[/*\"</span>其中某一项<span class=\"string\">\",\"</span>其中另外一项<span class=\"string\">\"*/]\"</span>)\t\t\t<span class=\"comment\">//以数组的形式赋值</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<blockquote><p>遍历节点会用到的几种方法<br>children()方法 用于取得匹配元素的子元素集合 PS：children()方法只考虑子元素不考虑任何后代元素<br>next()方法 用于取得匹配元素后面紧邻的一个同辈元素<br>prev()方法 用于取得匹配元素前面紧邻的一个同辈元素<br>siblings()方法 用于取得匹配元素前后紧邻的所有同辈元素<br>closest()方法  用于取得最近的匹配元素  首先检查当前元素是否匹配，如果匹配则返回元素本身，如果不匹配则向上查找父元素，逐级向上直到找到匹配选择器的元素，如果什么都没找到则返回一个空的JQuery对象</p>\n</blockquote>\n","categories":[{"name":"JavaSript","slug":"JavaSript","count":1,"path":"api/categories/JavaSript.json"},{"name":"JQuery","slug":"JavaSript/JQuery","count":1,"path":"api/categories/JavaSript/JQuery.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"笔记","slug":"笔记","count":6,"path":"api/tags/笔记.json"}]}